{"tid":154310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭智遇車禍缺席亞冠記者會","createTime":"2017-03-13T08:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T08:18:12.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f59612e37450e9ea5b5d5056bc7ac6da23e8c0","tid":154310,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:13:20.000Z","msg":"亞冠聯賽第三輪小組賽週二打響，廣州恆大主場迎戰日本的川崎前鋒。今天的賽前發布會上按照慣例是主教練斯科拉里和鄭智一同出席，但恆大隊長卻在下午2點發布會時間後遲遲都未能出席，在球隊工作人員都聯繫之下，才得知原來鄭智是因為路上遇到了輕微車禍不得不缺席發布會。"},{"pid":"7d4b3586619884d470fe943937bab0cbee6d49d2","tid":154310,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc0cd1075ffd49992df4f8a6d45b6f25367e3bc","tid":154310,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:15:19.000Z","msg":"車唔死?"},{"pid":"86599e92a378c642a3d95c96e2e0dc8b6129f1aa","tid":154310,"uid":33104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:17:00.000Z","msg":"又出絕招，怕輸扮病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20357af316de1197e6eb07935c5537a2f9f8faa3","tid":154310,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:17:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ff8562d2cbf0fce0585dbd4e464772274e4c53f","tid":154310,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:18:12.000Z","msg":"弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}